    <!-- about flippy section and strings -->
    <string name="title_activity_about">About Flippy</string>
    <string name="about_message_one">            Flippy is an app that allows you to share information among people in a community.
            At Flippy, a community is simply an established entity like a university or workplace.</string>
    <string name="about_message_two">Within a community, there are channels that you can subscribe to in order to get information from. These channels can simply be a class or a department.
            You can subscribe to channels that are outside of your community and you can also create a channel yourself.
            When you create a channel, you become the editor of the channel and you can assign four other people the role of an editor so that they help in posting information in the channel.</string>
    <string name="about_message_three">            Flippy is not a chat application but rather a notice board that information, gossip and announcement are posted on.
            Now, create channels and start posting.</string>
