    <!-- Help Activity Strings -->
    <string name="help_string_one">How do I create a channel ? \n\n
                   Draw out the navigation drawer
                   Click on channels then
                   add Channels. Enter Name, give short description and upload an image to represent it,
                   check/uncheck public (public channels can be seen by people outside your community, private channels can be accessed only by people inside your community)</string>
    <string name="help_string_two">How do I create a notice ? \n\n
            On the action bar Click on the “+” icon, Choose the Channel.
            Hurray, now you can create a Notice</string>
    <string name="help_string_three">        How do I subscribe to a channel ? \n\n
        To subscribe to a channel draw the navigation drawer,
        Choose My Community, this bring all the channels in your community as well as public channels in other communities.
        Click on the “Correct Sign ”(icon on the top left corner) to subscribe.</string>
    <string name="help_string_four">        How do I Manage a channel ? \n\n
        Draw the navigation drawer, Choose My Channels,  Click on the Channel to manage it (you must be an admin of a channel to manage it)</string>
